    "data": [
        {
            "title": "《破·地獄》3日內獲4項大獎備受各界肯定 加長版劇照首度曝光   谷德昭岑珈其登場大表期待",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"《破·地獄》加長版劇照首度曝光 3日內獲4項大獎備受各界肯定  谷德昭岑珈其登場大表期待\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/54dc4cb62645f13b8552202f2125dbe4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031322284832094.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">《破·地獄》加長版劇照首度曝光 3日內獲4項大獎備受各界肯定  谷德昭岑珈其登場大表期待</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>英皇電影《破·地獄》勇奪香港電影金像獎18項提名，刷新近十年提名紀錄，更先聲奪人於3日內奪得合共4項殊榮，包括《香港電影導演會年度大獎》中勇奪「最佳男主角（許冠文）」、「最佳女主角（衛詩雅）」及「最佳男配角（朱栢康）」，以及昨晚舉行之《香港電影編劇家協會》中，兩位編劇陳茂賢及鄭緯機共同榮獲「年度推薦劇本獎」。而將於4月4日清明節上映的《破·地獄》加長版，當中飾演美玉的周家怡有更多場面於加長版曝光，家怡說：「好開心有加長版嘅面世，可以圓滿每一個角色，能夠睇到佢哋嘅故事，包括道生家庭故事都會喺加長版入面見到。我最開心係會保持有光明嘅結局，即係美玉嘅BB仍然會保留住，仍然係咁圓滿。」\n\n</p><h2>谷德昭：與有榮焉</h2>\n<p>至於深受觀眾期待，於加長版首度登場的谷德昭及岑珈其對加長版同樣大表期待，跟子華及朱康同框演出的谷德昭表示：「能夠在《破·地獄》同大家見面，成為最高票房電影一份子，與有榮焉。」；而戲中跟子華「道生」一角飾演兩兄弟的珈其表示：「當知道加長版面世真係好開心同埋期待。之前導演有講過佢一定會極力爭取出返個加長版，所以我真係好多謝導演，而最最最最多謝都係咁多位買飛入場支持《破·地獄》嘅觀眾，因為係佢哋嘅支持先至會令到呢個加長版可以正式面世。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"《香港電影編劇家協會》在昨晚舉行，《破·地獄》依然大豐收。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e6b4c97eb4552d23f2a83ec12516aa71/2025-03/01_2.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《香港電影編劇家協會》在昨晚舉行，《破·地獄》依然大豐收。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"兩位編劇陳茂賢及鄭緯機共同榮獲「年度推薦劇本獎」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0b78aa83d90968ec27401e8d58121a85/2025-03/02_2_5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩位編劇陳茂賢及鄭緯機共同榮獲「年度推薦劇本獎」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳茂賢在台上分享感受。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2356661c92588a2644bf834ffb6bb4f8/2025-03/03_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳茂賢在台上分享感受。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"《破·地獄》榮獲「年度推薦劇本獎」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/edc8a5403f1a64d6b81b0bcb819fb1e3/2025-03/174187528893592.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《破·地獄》榮獲「年度推薦劇本獎」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"《破·地獄》加長版將於4月4日清明節上映。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ff5f1ff0069642846a3d5eb7e4521417/2025-03/DSC02739.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《破·地獄》加長版將於4月4日清明節上映。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"飾演美玉的周家怡透露，加長版保持有光明的結局，美玉的BB仍然會保留住。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/63de0a441a9590aa730cb096a395f333/2025-03/DSC04489.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        飾演美玉的周家怡透露，加長版保持有光明的結局，美玉的BB仍然會保留住。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"周家怡表示加場版結局好圓滿。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ae431ddd9294a99ba639171679420cbb/2025-03/DSC04496.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        周家怡表示加場版結局好圓滿。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"許冠文近日在《香港電影導演會年度大獎》中勇奪「最佳男主角」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/577bee7be4a67069daa091a79b98698d/2025-03/DSC05999.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        許冠文近日在《香港電影導演會年度大獎》中勇奪「最佳男主角」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"衛詩雅在《香港電影導演會年度大獎》中勇奪「最佳女主角」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2ad6ea638de915fad189313c357c0d5f/2025-03/DSC07214.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        衛詩雅在《香港電影導演會年度大獎》中勇奪「最佳女主角」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子華、朱栢康\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c8f6cc4f3fc9b5b2c6576c58f59b480d/2025-03/DSC07890.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子華、朱栢康\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"戲中跟子華「道生」一角演兩兄弟的珈其對於加長版面世好感動。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1f755828411621d6528ff445012d084d/2025-03/DSC08006.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戲中跟子華「道生」一角演兩兄弟的珈其對於加長版面世好感動。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"珈其表示能與子華神合作好夢幻。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/26cc8e0d762aab0d49403b4e4b27da10/2025-03/DSC09391-2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        珈其表示能與子華神合作好夢幻。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朱栢康在《香港電影導演會年度大獎》中勇奪「最佳男配角」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/907c36e6fab3bcadfea354f777d75a19/2025-03/DSC09493.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱栢康在《香港電影導演會年度大獎》中勇奪「最佳男配角」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"谷德昭對於加場版推出，他感到與有榮焉！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c120d5b40c85381caba0cd4a73214326/2025-03/DSC09689-2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        谷德昭對於加場版推出，他感到與有榮焉！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"谷德昭多謝買飛入場支持《破地獄》的觀眾。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8ae5fa5a2bed35b447a0b5400cc131e7/2025-03/DSC09777-2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        谷德昭多謝買飛入場支持《破地獄》的觀眾。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>與子華神合作好夢幻</h2>\n<p>而珈其亦大爆自己是子華鐵粉，有機會合作大感夢幻：「我可以見到子華哥哥超級開心，因為我係好鍾意佢，佢係我偶像之一，仲要可以同佢同場，記得拍攝前一晚真係緊張到瞓唔着，所以真係好多謝導演俾呢個機會我。成件事都係好夢幻，子華哥哥係超級 nice，拍攝前我哋一齊溝通傾偈呀，跟住一齊去試戲。所以成個過程係好開心好順利，希望加長版出到嚟大家觀眾都鍾意啦，多謝晒。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
